{"tid":1221301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好「係又衝，唔係又衝」，適當時要識走","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T19:25:55.000Z","uid":35870,"like":120,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c3135bdc233b2fb3192ef3fa6cfbb212ffd9bf59","tid":1221301,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:27:00.000Z","msg":"（此post純粹係遊擊戰學術研究，並不鼓勵大家做任何暴力犯法行為）<br />\n<br />\n話雖各有各做，但係希望唔好係唔係都將成個示威level升級，好似黎緊星期日，立法會唔洗開會，會黎嘅人包括一家大細有老有嫩有女人，真係完全無必要搞咩衝擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正如上星期日，大家入夜之後留守立法會政總外，其實都無咩太大意思，因為第二日又唔係要開會<br />\n<br />\n又好似星期三夜晚，其實都取消左個會好耐，但有班人唔知點解仲留係到，留到好夜，你霸佔緊d咩，佔領緊d咩呢？你得個小貓三四隻，係咪覺得你守到條防線呢？你守到係因為對面班警察廢事搞你，唔係你真係守到。個晚好彩d警察無捉人，如果唔係你地真係會死得好慘。<br />\n<br />\n反而星期三朝早就真係做到野，因為班立法會人要開會，衝擊佔領搞到佢開唔到會，其實係非常之成功（再一次帶頭盔：本人不鼓勵暴力衝擊行為純粹學術研究）。<br />\n<br />\n所以，衝之前真係要有個目的。係連登有時見到有d超級激進港獨份子，例如個位HKVDC_XXXX，係咁叫人係又衝唔係又衝，總之24小時同你不停衝就最好，都痴9線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學陳雲話齋，有時無必要堅持佔領某d地方，如果唔係，就會搞到好似2014咁，佔下佔下整左個佔領金鐘出黎，跟住佔到毫無意義，唔知為乜而佔<br />\n<br />\n所以，其實示威者反而要多謝警察，因為警察班on9執意要清場，星期日晚清左次，星期三又清左次，但同時要多謝班on9，無佢地清場嘅話，只會變成2014翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家輿論上警察係輸晒<br />\n<br />\n所以大家，學術上黎講，要係適當時先好衝，適當時就要走，呢個先係遊擊戰嘅思維"},{"pid":"7f3d43e3ea1a6093e84fae44b6d904a38b4d1701","tid":1221301,"uid":119455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638f17568771904bee20d17ebf2ca500090b9272","tid":1221301,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:37:18.000Z","msg":"時事台去post去得太快唔推唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd41836cf09808fc83553b9d2c7efcce6d5bf074","tid":1221301,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3d43e3ea1a6093e84fae44b6d904a38b4d1701","tid":1221301,"uid":119455,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:31:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba227654dbbd05e5ca91258dbe0ea8537e06f9d","tid":1221301,"uid":103585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e60afbf67784ac3cc658b1ee17a1cab685a3b443","tid":1221301,"uid":59016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6848829b4d64236e69f875bf95dd30322885ba95","tid":1221301,"uid":237747,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"同意，其實好多時無必要佔住條路，d狗趕就走，之後再堅持出返黎，可能仲能夠打擊d狗既士氣"},{"pid":"24544c26007d6d7718159fdbfc2212d5ebffa426","tid":1221301,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6848829b4d64236e69f875bf95dd30322885ba95","tid":1221301,"uid":237747,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"同意，其實好多時無必要佔住條路，d狗趕就走，之後再堅持出返黎，可能仲能夠打擊d狗既士氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:49:05.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"2e43526944f063e2b94a679c6a725131a296f6b6","tid":1221301,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696633e00757d102d1a2c33471f4241ede043102","tid":1221301,"uid":10637,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quot